response.original_title: Wonders Made By Man - Part 3 and 4
response.overview: The World abounds with beautiful structures created by mankind - cities, skyscrapers, edifices, memorials, places of worships, pieces of arts and crafts and even jewelry. 'Wonders Made by Man' takes us through a few known and many other completely unknown structures that most of us may never get to witness in person. Parts 3 and 4 visit Toltecs, Statue of Liberty, Taj Mahal, and more!
